    "Conversely, the lowest rates for both incidence and mortality are observed in regions south and west of London.",
    "Figure 3 displays the temporal trends of crude incidence and mortality rates per 100,000 inhabitants during the study years.",
    "We observe a relatively stable incidence rate throughout the study period, ranging between 105 and 120.",
    "In contrast, the mortality rate decreases linearly, starting around 100 crude rate and decreasing until 70.",
    "Thus, distinct temporal trends were observed between lung cancer incidence and mortality."
